channel.title: First sig attempt
channel.description: [IMG]http://i67.photobucket.com/albums/h313/googleit2/sigattempt2.jpg[/img] Any suggestions on making it suck less? (also, i made it in gimp cause i'm a cheap bastard...) [IMG]http://i67.photobucket.com/albums/h313/googleit2/sigattempt.jpg[/img] Here's a similar, brighter version wit some different coloring, kinda different brushing, and a modified render. I'm currently working on a much nicer looking version that is something of a blend of these two, with the second render and many more brushes. EDIT:i finally got photoshop, and here was my result: [IMG]http://i67.photobucket.com/albums/h313/googleit2/goog_coolsig.jpg[/img] I thought it looked nicer but...tis not my decision, now is it?
